Thematic Evaluation: The retrieved data was classified into key research domains: legacy mainframe constraints, microservices and cloud-native taxonomies, vendor comparison, relational database models, transaction consistency, and risk-mitigation strategies.

Conceptual Integration: The analyzed data was synthesized into narrative prose and structured tables. This approach integrates technical specifications with business and regulatory analysis, offering a comprehensive assessment of modern Core Banking Solutions without utilizing active code scripts.







